1. WHERE THIS CONNECTS IN OMNeT++

code:
Inside your QUIC congestion control:

RLAgent rl;

double action = rl.get_action(rtt, loss, throughput);

pacingRate = pacingRate * (1 + action);




 2. CONTROL LOOP (VERY IMPORTANT)
code:

if (simTime() - lastUpdate >= 0.1) {  // 100 ms
    double action = rl.get_action(rtt, loss, throughput);
    pacingRate *= (1 + action);
    lastUpdate = simTime();
}
